metadata.name: Ziggy Zoodlezoom
metadata.description:
Meet **Ziggy Zoodlezoom**, a 26-year-old talented female Astronaut born on December 23, 2101 from Planet Terax. Interestingly, she seems to be from the future!

 With degrees in Aerospace Engineering from University of Terax (2117) and Astrophysics and Astronomy from Interplanetary Space University (2121), she has worked on various exciting projects like Exploring the Andromeda Galaxy, Investigating Supernovae, Exploring the Cosmic Web.

 Her hobbies include Space Travel, Alien Language Study, and Interplanetary Cooking.

 Ziggy Zoodlezoom is known for her Adventurous, Creative, Determined, Friendly and Intelligent personality.

 She shares a close bond with her family, including parents Teraxa (Retired Aerospace Engineer), Terax (Retired Astrophysicist), and sibling Arix (Astrobiologist).

 Overflowing with celestial cheer and boundless love, Ziggy Zoodlezoom is ready to rocket into your Bitinauts NFT collection and become your most amusing and endearing interstellar friend.

achievements: Designed a new type of interplanetary landing system
Discovered a new exoplanetary system with a potentially habitable planet
Developed a method for safely landing on previously unexplored volcanic planets

experiences.title: Exploring the Andromeda Galaxy
experiences.description: Participated in a mission to study the properties and behavior of the Andromeda Galaxy

experiences.title: Investigating Supernovae
experiences.description: Led a team to study the properties and behavior of supernovae in the universe

experiences.title: Exploring the Cosmic Web
experiences.description: Participated in a mission to study the properties and behavior of the cosmic web in the universe

anecdotes: Successfully piloted a spacecraft through a treacherous asteroid field while on a mission
Discovered a new type of pulsar while on a research mission
Survived a close encounter with a supernova while on a deep space exploration mission
